Introducing <b>Starla</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Starla's a long-time resident of Millsberry. She's been at <a href='/home/?user=cstara'>25655 Central Avenue</a>, in Metro Park, since July 10, 2005.<br><br>Some say there's nothing like Metro Park, and Starla would totally agree. She loves being right in the heart of Millsberry, and is a huge fan of living only steps away from the Downtown Entertainment Complex. <br><br>And we might as well call Starla "The Master" because she has so many Master Trophies in her bedroom, you have to wonder where she sleeps! <br><br>When Starla's not rocking challenges and games, she likes to decorate her house with some of the coolest stuff in Millsberry. <br><br>You can also see from all the flowers and gardening tools that Starla has a green thumb. Hers is one of the nicest backyards in town.<br><br>Starla describes herself as very friendly, a little outgoing, and smart. Looking at her trophies, and the awesome rooms in her house, you can tell that she's competitive and creative, too.<br><br>Stop by and say 'Hi' to Starla some time. She's one of the citizens that makes Millsberry so great!<br></div>
